# pdfmake 的使用教程

## 安装

```bash
npm install pdfmake
```

Notice: `pdfmake` 原本并不支持中文需要引入中文字体.

## 引入中文字体

思源字体下载地址:

```bash
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adobe-fonts/source-han-sans/release/OTF/SimplifiedChinese/SourceHanSansSC-Regular.otf
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adobe-fonts/source-han-sans/release/OTF/SimplifiedChinese/SourceHanSansSC-Bold.otf
```

使用 `pdfmake` 项目中的 `build-vfs.js` 文件, 构建字体相关的 js 文件, 生成的文件 `build/vfs_fonts.js`

```js
import pdfMake from "pdfmake/build/pdfmake";
// 引入项目中原有的字体文件
import pdfFonts from "pdfmake/build/vfs_fonts";
// 引入思源字体文件
import scFonts from "./vfs_fonts";

// 导入
pdfMake.vfs = { ...pdfFonts.pdfMake.vfs, ...scFonts.pdfMake.vfs };
// 设置
pdfMake.fonts = {
  Roboto: {
    normal: "Roboto-Regular.ttf",
    bold: "Roboto-Medium.ttf",
    italics: "Roboto-Italic.ttf",
    bolditalics: "Roboto-Italic.ttf",
  },
  SourceHanSans: {
    normal: "SourceHanSansSC-Regular.otf",
    bold: "SourceHanSansSC-Bold.otf",
    italics: "SourceHanSansSC-Regular.otf",
    bolditalics: "SourceHanSansSC-Bold.otf",
  },
};
```

## 使用

```js
// 创建一个文档定义对象
// 定义文档内容
var docDefinition = {
  content: [
    { text: "PDFMake示例", style: "header" },
    { text: "这是一个PDF文档生成示例", style: "subheader" },
    { text: "下面是一个表格示例：" },
    {
      table: {
        headers: ["名称", "数量", "价格"],
        body: [
          ["商品1", 1, "$10"],
          ["商品2", 2, "$20"],
          ["商品3", 3, "$30"],
        ],
      },
    },
    {
      image: "data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQEASABIAAD...",
    },
  ],
  styles: {
    header: {
      fontSize: 22,
      bold: true,
    },
    subheader: {
      fontSize: 18,
      bold: true,
    },
    customfont: {
      fontSize: 12,
      font: "SourceHanSans",
    },
  },
  defaultStyle: {
    font: "SourceHanSans",
  },
};

// 生成PDF文档
const pdfDocGenerator = pdfMake.createPdf(docDefinition);

// 导出PDF文档
pdfDocGenerator.download("output.pdf");
```

## 在 vue 中使用

```vue
<template>
  <view class="pdf-make-wrapper">
    <view class="btn" @click="click">btn</view>
  </view>
</template>

<script>
import pdfMake from "pdfmake/build/pdfmake";
import pdfFonts from "pdfmake/build/vfs_fonts";

import scFonts from "./vfs_fonts";
pdfMake.vfs = { ...pdfFonts.pdfMake.vfs, ...scFonts.pdfMake.vfs };
pdfMake.fonts = {
  Roboto: {
    normal: "Roboto-Regular.ttf",
    bold: "Roboto-Medium.ttf",
    italics: "Roboto-Italic.ttf",
    bolditalics: "Roboto-Italic.ttf",
  },
  SourceHanSans: {
    normal: "SourceHanSansSC-Regular.otf",
    bold: "SourceHanSansSC-Bold.otf",
    italics: "SourceHanSansSC-Regular.otf",
    bolditalics: "SourceHanSansSC-Bold.otf",
  },
};

export default {
  name: "PdfMake",
  data() {
    return {};
  },
  created() {
    logger.log("pdfMake.vfs:", pdfMake.vfs);
  },
  methods: {
    click() {
      logger.log("test click...");

      // 创建一个文档定义对象
      // 定义文档内容
      var docDefinition = {
        content: [
          { text: "PDFMake示例", style: "header" },
          { text: "这是一个PDF文档生成示例", style: "subheader" },
          { text: "下面是一个表格示例：" },
          {
            table: {
              headers: ["名称", "数量", "价格"],
              body: [
                ["商品1", 1, "$10"],
                ["商品2", 2, "$20"],
                ["商品3", 3, "$30"],
              ],
            },
          },
          {
            image:
              "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
          },
        ],
        styles: {
          header: {
            fontSize: 22,
            bold: true,
          },
          subheader: {
            fontSize: 18,
            bold: true,
          },
          customfont: {
            fontSize: 12,
            font: "SourceHanSans",
          },
        },
        defaultStyle: {
          font: "SourceHanSans",
        },
      };

      // 生成PDF文档
      const pdfDocGenerator = pdfMake.createPdf(docDefinition);

      // 导出PDF文档
      pdfDocGenerator.download("output.pdf");
    },
  },
};
</script>

```
